 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地好需要大家都Like我地FB同簽名去嚮應呀！！</span></span><br />\nFACEBOOK PAGE <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%2F&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=af619cd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/byebuydayhk/</a><br />\n簽署ＬＩＮＫ 一定要簽 <a href=\"https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbyebuydayhk.github.io%2Fbyebuydayweb%2Fpledge.html&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=d572d854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://byebuydayhk.github.io/byebuydayweb/pledge.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買可以好有效</span></strong><br />\n如果香港有200萬人=2/7.5人口每星期少2日購物 = 2/7.5*2/7 = 少10%營業額，對鋪租貴既香港地，10%營業額分分鍾就等於商家既50%淨利。另外, 個人消費佔左香港GDP既68%, 如果少10%既消費就等於少左10%既GDP。<br />\n下一季度GPD再負增長,香港將進入Technical Recession。政府冇得唔理。<br />\n<br />\n更加有學者研究指出，罷買只需要全港252,000人集中一日不消費，經濟就會受到好大影響。 (BBC： The '3.5% rule:' How a small minority can change the world.)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷買內容（好簡單）</span></strong><br />\n1. 逄星期五、日不花費於日常必須以外的消費<br />\n2. 逄星期五、日不在外食 (上班人士午餐除非可以帶返否則難以避免，但晚餐回家進餐都十分有幫助)<br />\n3. 同時呼籲不光顧抵制清單內的企業，就算買日用品/其他消費都只幫襯良心/本土/外資企業<br />\n4. 呼籲推己及人, 例如絲打比仔仔約逢星期五、日出街食飯，同佢地講逄星期五、日罷買，或只揀良心企業<br />\n由上述基本概念，長遠減低整體消費。<br />\n<br />\n關於我地既報導：<br />\n眾新聞：I Banker（虛構）與網民發起逢周五、日罷買：零成本，希望和理非響應<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zpstHS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zpstHS&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=f9082172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zpstHS</a><br />\nＳＣＭＰ既報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U7zPJC&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=64295714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U7zPJC</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/1ta7DfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ta7DfO.jpg&h=470d5d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/5OkGHHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5OkGHHu.jpg&h=ee06cc13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_oc=AQngPLH6GmE4BKFF48gvVpRu1WGq5B0lkOOlA8n2pvxmkZUQCiqDIPvyo6SNlRMiDeU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=3a6e2ea0543ac7cbe4e916d256f537f0&amp;oe=5DD82060\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67929653_112049723486814_8982519114232758272_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_oc%3DAQngPLH6GmE4BKFF48gvVpRu1WGq5B0lkOOlA8n2pvxmkZUQCiqDIPvyo6SNlRMiDeU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D3a6e2ea0543ac7cbe4e916d256f537f0%26oe%3D5DD82060&h=80325f8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75d3062dcdab7bba95991d89b8e3ede5f520a9f3","tid":1516714,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a61fbb993c815b10878a334c4aca6de75931e4f9","tid":1516714,"uid":222251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:14:03.000Z","msg":"食蕉啦<br />\n<br />\n罷食！有餐廳老闆話想考警察拎警棍幫人教仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281596</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T16:24:34.000Z","msg":"係我唔好無做資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以唔推啦"},{"pid":"f8a75fb045e190b52df9ce66870453f8e23d58d2","tid":1516714,"uid":46457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T1